The slice() method in SAPUI5/JavaScript is used to extract a portion of an array or string into a new shallow copy without modifying the original, using arr.slice(start, end). It is commonly used in SAPUI5 controllers to copy data from a JSON model, manipulate subsets of arrays, or format strings.
